description:
&lt;p&gt;Weqas is one of the largest External Quality Assessment (EQA) providers in the United Kingdom with over 600 clients providing services to both laboratory and POCT diagnostic services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a motivated, courteous receptionist to provide an effective and friendly front line support service (both face to face and by telephone) to visitors and staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The receptionist will be the front line, first contact experience for Weqas; the post holder should be warm, friendly, welcoming, and knowledgeable and be able to demonstrate a caring attitude.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The duties performed by the Receptionist will be:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To provide a helpful and informative customer focused reception service as the initial point of contact for clients and visitors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Answer general enquiries or seek appropriate advice to ensure all internal or external service users receive appropriate and accurate information.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To deal with all internal &amp; external calls appropriately and in an efficient and courteous manner, resolving any queries where possible. Transferring enquiries to the appropriate team for technical advice, or passing on messages to the appropriate member(s) of staff.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure goods are received appropriately into the building in compliance with goods receipt procedure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To undertake clerical duties, including photocopying, as requested by management and be flexible in approach to work should the need arise.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ensuring standard reception and admin duties are fulfilled and representing Weqas in a professional manner at all times is critical to this post.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date: 19/11/2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Laura Lloyd-Lewis&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Marketing Manager&lt;/p&gt;
